content: come get your free holiday pattern from little muggles this little cutie adds a pop of kawaii cuteness to your holidays use it as an ornament for your tree or on a gift or as room decor it s too adorable not to make it s a quick and easy project that can be finished in a relatively short period of time have fun and don t forget to visit little muggles from time to time to see other fun projects and patterns xoxo
